OL,3,CRival Indian restaurants in legal
OL,4,Cdispute over origin of butter chicken
OL,5,Cdish
OL,7,FTwo restaurants in India are in the
OL,8,Fmiddle of a legal dispute over the
OL,9,Fright to call themselves the home of
OL,10,Fthe original recipe for butter chicken.
OL,12,FThe dish is one of the most popular
OL,13,Fcurries in the world, made with .
OL,15,FIt is dubbed one of and one of the
OL,16,Fmost popular curries in the UK.
OL,18,FThe cuisine though is at the centre of
OL,19,Fa legal fight, as the two eateries
OL,20,FDelhi Moti Mahal and Daryaganj both
OL,21,Fclaim they were the first to create it.
