OL,7,FThe lawsuit to decide the matter was
OL,8,Fbrought by the family who run Moti
OL,9,FMahal.
OL,11,FMoti Mahal claim
OL,13,FAccording to the Gujral family, the
OL,14,Fdish was the creation of their
OL,15,Fgrandfather Kundan Lal Gujral who
OL,16,Ffounded the restaurant in Peshawar, in
OL,17,Fwhat is now Pakistan.
OL,19,FAfter India was split during partition
OL,20,Fin 1947, they moved the restaurant to
OL,21,FDelhi.
