OL,7,FThey say the recipe, an indulgent
OL,8,Fcurry that involves tender pieces of
OL,9,Fchicken cooked in a tandoor oven mixed
OL,10,Finto a rich tomato gravy laden with
OL,11,Fbutter and cream, was invented by
OL,12,FGujral in the 1930s to use up leftover
OL,13,Ftandoor chicken.
OL,15,FDaryaganj claim
OL,17,FRival restaurant Daryaganj has also
OL,18,Fstaked its claim to butter chicken's
OL,19,Forigins.
