OL,5,Cdish
OL,7,FThe restaurant owners say their
OL,8,Frelative, Kundan Lal Jaggi, had worked
OL,9,Fwith Gujral when he moved his
OL,10,Frestaurant to Delhi in 1947.
OL,12,FAnd it was there that butter chicken
OL,13,Fwas created.
OL,15,FThis, they say, gives them the right
OL,16,Fto call themselves home to the first
OL,17,Fserving of the dish, a claim they say
OL,18,Fthey trademarked in 2018.
OL,20,FWhat's next?
